title: Ep. #56 | Catching Up: Lauv
description:
This week, Lauv joins the Daebak fam to discuss his new album ~how I’m feeling~ as well as his journey to becoming a musician. Lauv also shares his thoughts on mental health and his experience collaborating with BTS.
Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios
